doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    title Movie Selection
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.0/css/bulma.min.css')
  body
    include ../partials/nav.pug
    include ../partials/modal.pug
    // SECTION FOR HERO BELOW NAVBAR
    section.hero.is-medium.is-primary.is-bold
      .hero-body.has-text-centered
        .container
          h1.title
            | The database of any movie
          h2.subtitle
            | Deciding what movie to watch? Let us help you
          form#searchMovie
            input.input.is-rounded.is-medium(type='text' placeholder='Type in a movie!')
            input#movieSearch.button(type='submit' value='Search')
    // Content section for title within the body
    section
      .content.is-large.has-text-centered.pt-6.pb-6
        h1 What's popular now?
    .columns.is-3.is-centered
      .column.is-one-third
        a(href='/movieSingle.html')
        .card
          a(href='/movieSingle.html')
            .card-image
              figure.image.is-4by3
                img(src= moviesToShow[0].Poster)
          header.card-header
            a(href='/movieSingle.html')
              p.card-header-title
                | Fellowship of the Ring
            a.card-header-icon(href='#' aria-label='more options')
              span.icon
                i.fas.fa-angle-down(aria-hidden='true')
          .card-content
            .content
              | An epic journey about a buncha people defending this hobbit with a ring. 
              br
              br
              br
              |               Rating: 10/10
              br
              |               Run Time: 3:15 hours (extended edition)
              br
              |               Release Year: 2001
              br
      // ------------------------------
      .column.is-one-third
        a(href='/movieSingle.pug')
        .card
          a(href='/movieSingle.pug')
            .card-image
              figure.image.is-4by3
                img(src='https://bulma.io/images/placeholders/1280x960.png' alt='Placeholder image')
          header.card-header
            a(href='/movieSingle.pug')
              p.card-header-title
                | The Two Towers
            a.card-header-icon(href='#' aria-label='more options')
              span.icon
                i.fas.fa-angle-down(aria-hidden='true')
          .card-content
            .content
              | The hobbit got lost, but the journey ain't over. 
              | An epic battle, a long walk, and two hungry hobbits 
